    <h1>Events - Module</h1>
        <p>Events provides the power to add various events including image collections and a write up about an event. This can be done before or after the event and be displayed with a user friendly experience. Similar to a blog the user has various WYSIWYG elements and a simple UI. You can view all the events in both a calendar format and a list format.</p>
